description: CAMO is a privacy network contract grafted under Ethereum. The Alpha version will be released this month. -When the user transfers money using the CAMO contract, the token will be transferred in the random privacy wallet, and the addresses of the sender and receiver will be anonymous. -The Deep Modes privacy layer of CAMO also allows users to visit websites, Defi and DAPP completely anonymously as mirror images. -The first DAPP game based on the CAMO contract is under development. Users will be able to transfer funds anonymously and retrieve smart contracts.
name: Camouflage.eth
